    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/b863afa1932302d169d7975d84a95f18.poster.avif?t=1765490959\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/b863afa1932302d169d7975d84a95f18.webm?t=1765490959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/b863afa1932302d169d7975d84a95f18.mp4?t=1765490959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>准备好拯救众神了吗？</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valkyrie Rising: Hordes of Ragnarök 是一款北欧风格的生存类Roguelite游戏。迎战无尽的诸神黄昏军团，探索手工打造的地图，强化你的技能并升级武器，活得越久越强！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/06278e4e72b588d679fbd600eee4c90c.poster.avif?t=1765490959\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/06278e4e72b588d679fbd600eee4c90c.webm?t=1765490959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/06278e4e72b588d679fbd600eee4c90c.mp4?t=1765490959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>升级，再升级！</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >斩杀敌人、获取经验并升级。每次强化都随机生成，效果各异，让每一轮冒险都充满未知！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/a5e06305018c28e4835f9316361ce467.poster.avif?t=1765490959\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/a5e06305018c28e4835f9316361ce467.webm?t=1765490959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/a5e06305018c28e4835f9316361ce467.mp4?t=1765490959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成任务，获得奥丁、托尔等神灵的祝福。释放闪电、召唤天界武器，或让大地在敌人脚下崩裂！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/69163362eb3f95d216bcb6fe645ccf60.poster.avif?t=1765490959\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/69163362eb3f95d216bcb6fe645ccf60.webm?t=1765490959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214330/extras/69163362eb3f95d216bcb6fe645ccf60.mp4?t=1765490959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>游戏特色：</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对抗无尽的敌群，包括强大的Boss与精英敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取经验并不断变强</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过任务引导神力，掌握强大神技</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索阿斯加德破碎的世界与手工制作的地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创造需要精准操作的自定义技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强化武器，解锁全新战斗风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次挑战后解锁永久升级，持续变强</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
